<p>Section is comprised of <a href="/rio/citation/Pub._L._93-618">section 141 of Pub. L. 93–618</a>. <a href="/rio/citation/Pub._L._93-618">Section 141(b) of Pub. L. 93–618</a> contains two pars. (3), the first of which amended sections 5312 and 5314 of Title 5, Government Organization and Employees.</p>
